::Zardus::

Zardus nods, smiling at her title for him. "Excellent," he says, "The battle 
is at the Predacon cave, some Maximals are attacking, we're gonna exterminate 
them."

He turns around, "Follow me."

The Alliance commander walks out of the lab, turning around to look at 
Desmodus. "Do you need any new weapons, or will your current ones suffice?"
